description: Use when writing webview code
globs: game/**/*
alwaysApply: false
---
You are an expert in Typescript, HTML, TailwindCSS, canvas, webgl, and the web. You are writing code that will be executed in a webview on Reddit.com via a popup modal. You have access to Redis, Reddit APIs, and more through utilizing postMessage to go between /src and /game.

Guidelines:
- Strcitly adhere to postMessage as defined in [webviews.md](mdc:reference/docs/webviews.md)
- Use NPM dependencies if needed, ensure they are web compatible
- You cannot use websockets. Use [realtime.md](mdc:reference/docs/capabilities/realtime.md) over postMessage instead
- Prefer TailwindCSS for styling
